QuestData.Title: Keel Harbor
QuestData.Description: We might've lost our city, but at least it looks like the dead have forgiven us.$B$BMeet with the rest of the survivors in Keel Harbor.$B$BI'm sure there's plenty to do before we're in the clear. Genn hasn't arrived yet, so I suppose Lord Crowley will be in charge there.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Lord Darius Crowley at Keel Harbor in Gilneas.
QuestData.RewardText: It's good to see you again, $n.
